s/s1600/death-wish-bruce-willis.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ib8C3Io5KS0%2FWk-GvgYmVCI%2FAAAAAAAAVGI%2FD6lQvn7tUPMv7Bie_Bv2lItPWxNpNNQ5QCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fdeath-wish-bruce-willis.jpg&h=99a74277&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.一名為曾為政府工作的前中情局成員化名為羅柏&middot;麥考現住在麻薩諸塞州的波士頓，並在一間五金賣場上班。他協助他的同事朋友拉爾夫減重，以便通過保安考試。麥考答應已過世的妻子，絕不會再回到過去的危險生活。因妻子生前很愛看書，麥考為了達到讀滿100本書，下班後他習慣帶著一包茶包到住家附近一間餐廳看書，日復一日，過著平靜的生活..<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述當原本一個位在芝加哥的幸福美滿的家庭遭歹徒闖入，女主人為此喪命，而女兒則遭到強暴、在心中蒙上陰影。這使得該家庭的男主人保羅感到悲痛欲絕，在警方靠不住的情況下，他決定化身為殘酷的私刑者，並不計一切代價追擊兇手；與此同時，他也就此成為了伸張私刑正義的街頭英雄..<br />\n<br />\n10 40PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=lZkW6VhE5WN5Wr719NYtii7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=17ea0484\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=lZkW6VhE5WN5Wr719NYtii7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=a1d37e39\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca90a0d8d3f5f548865be001915102711ad9b7db","tid":674290,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4634ed31b4c570851bdd82de4c9155db7911f6","tid":674290,"uid":41605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-2